e_wolf: pic#56843722","article":"Not even close to caught up, but wanted to let you know your Wild Cards posts finally got me into the series; finished the first book and am on about the third or fourth story (depending on how counting)in Aces High. <br /><br />Was happily surprised to see Roger Zelazny stories (I met him once, at a book signing in 1990 at Dangerous Visions in LA, very nice man!), and also several of my favorites were by writers I'd never heard of before (and given how long ago the first Wild Cards came out, possibly never again). The Carrie Vaughn story was neat too and I'm holding out hopes to see more of Ghost Girl, even though it will probably be difficult given that the character was added over 20 years after the volume came out. <br /><br />Also major thank you for your touting Arrival -- finally saw it earlier tonight, wonderful film!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 months ago","ctime":"February 9 2017, 11:17:29 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://mojave-wolf.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"mojave_wolf","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"mojave_wolf","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://mojave-wolf.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"mojave_wolf","ctime_ts":1486639049,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/91237832/7059164","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/520414.html?thread=25730526#t25730526","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/520414.html?thread=25730526#t25730526","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/520414.html?thread=25730526#t25730526","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"